# product-self-knowledge Skill — Dreamcobots Platform

## What is Dreamcobots?

Dreamcobots is an AI-powered bot platform built by **DreamCo Technologies**. It provides a collection of specialized automation bots organized by industry, use case, and skill domain. The platform enables:

- **Business automation** — invoicing, proposals, CRM tasks
- **Financial workflows** — budgets, expense tracking, financial models
- **Marketing content** — social posts, campaigns, SEO copy
- **Real estate** — listing descriptions, client communications, market analysis
- **Side hustles** — freelance automation, passive income tools
- **Government contracts** — RFP responses, compliance documentation
- **Education tools** — curriculum generation, student feedback
- **Healthcare tools** — clinical summaries, patient education content
- **Global AI** — multi-language support, international workflows

---

## Repository Structure

```
Dreamcobots/
├── bots/                     # Core bot implementations
├── App_bots/                 # Application-specific bots
├── Business_bots/            # Business workflow bots
├── Marketing_bots/           # Marketing automation
├── Fiverr_bots/              # Freelance platform bots
├── Real_Estate_bots/         # Real estate bots
├── Side_Hustle_bots/         # Side hustle automation
├── Government_Contract_bots/ # GovCon automation
├── Occupational_bots/        # Job/occupation tools
├── java_bots/                # Java-based bots
├── python_bots/              # Python-based bots
├── ai/                       # AI integration layer
├── api/                      # Backend API endpoints
├── frontend/                 # Web UI
├── marketplace/              # AIMarketplace integration
├── dashboard/                # DivisionDashboard + DreamCo dashboards
├── analytics-elites/         # Analytics tooling
├── integrations/             # Third-party integrations
├── src/                      # Core source modules
├── public/                   # Static assets & Copilot skills
├── docs/                     # Documentation
└── tests/                    # Test suite
```

---

## Key Modules

| Module | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `BuddyAI/` | Conversational AI assistant companion |
| `GlobalAI/` | Multi-language AI capabilities |
| `DreamFinance/` | Financial analysis and automation |
| `BusinessLaunchPad/` | End-to-end business launch workflows |
| `ConnectionsControl/` | CRM and networking automation |
| `DivisionDashboard/` | Per-division metrics and management |
| `AutoBotFactory/` | Bot creation and templating engine |
| `AIMarketplace/` | Marketplace for buying/selling bot services |
| `compliance/` | Regulatory compliance tooling |
| `dreamco-control-tower/` | Central orchestration and monitoring |

